title: Oldies but Goldies - 1740+ Classic DOS & Windows games
description:
This is my little collection of classic DOS and Windows games. There&#039;s over 1740 of them in one rar-package. Hope that you&#039;ll like it... :))

The full list of games included is just too long to put right here so it&#039;s downloadable at : http://www.mediafire.com/?yingpbnjtnn

Most of the games requires DOSBox to run correctly in modern PC&#039;s. DOSBox is freeware and I strongly recommend to download it from : http://www.downloadsource.net/2788/DOSBox/

I&#039;m seeding this one as often and as long as I possibly can. If you&#039;re downloading; SEED IT, please and THX! :)

CONTAINS NO VIRUSES OR MALWARE!
